│ ## Initial Observations ##                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ The reproducer is already minimized. Based on my experience in debugging these bugs, the issue is likely introduced by the *first transformation*, or due to incorrect analysis information feeding into it.   │
│ Here, the *first transformation* means the *first transformation point* that modifies the IR in the pass regardless of whether it's in the `vector-combine` module or other modules.                           │
│ #### Opt Information ####                                                                                                                                                                                      │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ To gather more insight, I ran `opt` to inspect both the transformations and the analysis results. Below are the command and the resulting log:                                                                 │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                        │
│ $ bin/opt --passes=vector-combine -S --debug-only=vector-combine /tmp/reprod__f1y0htt.ll                                                                                                                       │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ VECTORCOMBINE on src_1_idx                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ VC: Visiting:   %ld = load <16 x i8>, ptr %q, align 16                                                                                                                                                         │
│ VC: Visiting:   %v1 = insertelement <16 x i8> %ld, i8 %s, i1 %idx                                                                                                                                              │
│ VC: Visiting:   store <16 x i8> %v1, ptr %q, align 16                                                                                                                                                          │
│ opt: llvm/include/llvm/ADT/APInt.h:127: llvm::APInt::APInt(unsigned int, uint64_t, bool, bool): Assertion `llvm::isUIntN(BitWidth, val) && "Value is not an N-bit unsigned value"' failed.                     │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ ```                                                                                                                                                                                                            │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ From this log, I identified the first transformation point as:                                                                                                                                                 │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ ```                                                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/VectorCombine.cpp::canScalarizeAccess()                                                                                                                                          │
│ ```                                                                                                                                                                                                            │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ Here is the relevant backtrace at the moment of the transformation:                                                                                                                                            │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ ```stack                                                                                                                                                                                                       │
│ (frame 2) llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/VectorCombine.cpp:1450 in canScalarizeAccess                                                                                                                           │
│ (frame 3) llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/VectorCombine.cpp:1522 in (anonymous namespace)::VectorCombine::foldSingleElementStore                                                                                 │
│ (frame 4) llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/VectorCombine.cpp:3531 in operator()                                                                                                                                   │
